Had to redo my old work from a awhile back. The rose got allergic reaction from a numbing spray. That numbing spray company had a recalled and it was discontinue. I stop using all numbing spray because I had seen about 3-4 clients that had similar allergic reaction to the numbing spray. 
I still use numbing cream at the beginning of a tattoo only. The client brings their own. But our shop will start carrying the trusted brand soon. Never seen any bad reaction from the numbing cream yet. Hope this help.
